{
  "texts": [
    "See more in Appendix A.1.",
    "Note that although in-text citations can be hard to obtain for training, the key information lists are often provided in existing datasets.",
    "For each item in the list, we assign a reward of +w 1 if it is in the response, and -w 1 otherwise.",
    "We then sum up the rewards for all list items to obtain the reward for the whole response.Citation Recall R 2.",
    "Citation Recall is the percentage of sentences in the model response that can be supported by the corresponding cited passages."
  ]
}